---

**Step 2 — Deploy to Vercel**

Connect the repo to a new Vercel project. Add these environment variables:
```
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY          sk_live_... (Stripe Dashboard → Developers → API Keys)
STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET      get this in Step 3
FACEBOOK_PIXEL_ID          2055998351875626
FACEBOOK_ACCESS_TOKEN      EAAMSYJsmyKQ...
```

Deploy it. Your webhook URL will be:
```
https://promptwire-webhook.vercel.app/api/stripe-webhook
